    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Institutions that collect and care for living aquatic animals and plants, often in tanks, for purposes of observation, study, and display.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
